#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:4
msgid "Rigid Body"
msgstr "刚体"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:9
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:11
msgid ""
"This add-on uses Blender's built-in Rigid Body system for physics "
"simulation, so all parameters behave exactly as they do in Blender's "
"native Rigid Body settings."
msgstr ""
"本插件使用 Blender 内置的 **刚体系统（Rigid Body System）** 进行物理模拟，因此所有参数的行为与 Blender "
"原生刚体的设置完全一致。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:14
msgid ""
"If you are already familiar with these parameters, you may skip this "
"section."
msgstr "如果你已经熟悉这些参数，可以跳过本节。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:16
msgid ""
"Otherwise, the following sections provide a practical overview of the key"
" parameters along with real-world usage tips."
msgstr "否则，下面的内容将对几个关键参数进行简要说明，并结合实际使用经验提供一些调整建议。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:21
msgid "Mass"
msgstr "质量（Mass）"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:22
msgid ""
"The **Mass** parameter defines the inertia of an object, i.e. its "
"resistance to acceleration."
msgstr "**Mass（质量）** 参数定义了物体的惯性，即物体对加速度变化的抵抗程度。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:24
msgid ""
"**Acceleration response**: With the same applied force, heavier objects "
"accelerate more slowly."
msgstr "**加速度响应**：在施加相同力的情况下，质量越大的物体加速越慢。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:25
msgid ""
"**Collision behavior**: A high-mass object will push lighter ones aside "
"while being barely affected itself (conservation of momentum)."
msgstr "**碰撞行为**：质量较大的物体会更容易推动质量较小的物体，而自身受到的影响较小（动量守恒）。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:26
msgid ""
"**Gravity**: Mass does not change the free-fall speed (gravity is "
"constant), but it does affect impact forces."
msgstr "**重力影响**：质量不会改变自由落体速度（重力加速度恒定），但会影响碰撞时产生的冲击力。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:27
msgid ""
"**Rotational inertia**: Heavier objects are also harder to rotate due to "
"larger inertia tensors."
msgstr "**转动惯量**：质量较大的物体通常具有更大的惯性张量，因此更难被旋转。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:30
msgid ""
"The default value of ``1.0`` is neutral — you can treat it as a baseline "
"and adjust other objects relative to it."
msgstr "默认值 ``1.0`` 可以视为一个基准值，你可以以此为参考，根据需要对其他物体进行相对调整。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:35
msgid "Friction"
msgstr "摩擦力（Friction）"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:36
msgid ""
"**Friction** controls how much resistance occurs when a Rigid Body slides"
" across another surface."
msgstr "**Friction（摩擦力）** 控制刚体在另一个表面上滑动时产生的阻力大小。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:38
msgid "Higher values mean more resistance; objects slow down faster."
msgstr "数值越高，阻力越大，物体会更快停止。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:39
msgid "Lower values mean smoother surfaces, objects slide more easily."
msgstr "数值越低，表面越光滑，物体更容易滑动。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:41
msgid ""
"Blender uses its built-in Bullet physics engine to simulate Rigid Body "
"dynamics. The engine computes the combined friction between two objects "
"using Bullet's default formula:"
msgstr ""
"Blender 使用内置的 **Bullet 物理引擎（Bullet Physics Engine）** "
"来模拟刚体动力学。两个物体之间的综合摩擦力由 Bullet 使用如下公式计算："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:44
#, python-brace-format
msgid "friction_{total} = \\sqrt{friction_A \\times friction_B}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:48
msgid ""
"In practice, this means that if either object has a very low friction "
"value, the resulting combined friction will also be low. Both objects "
"must have sufficiently high friction values for the interaction to "
"provide strong resistance."
msgstr "在实际计算中，如果其中一个物体的摩擦值非常低，最终得到的综合摩擦力也会较低。只有当两个物体都具有较高摩擦值时，接触时才会产生明显的阻力。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:53
msgid "``0.0``: ice-like surface, endless sliding."
msgstr "``0.0``：类似冰面，几乎无限滑动。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:54
msgid "``0.2``: slippery floor, slow stop."
msgstr "``0.2``：较滑的地面，缓慢停止。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:55
msgid "``0.5``: typical wood or desktop friction."
msgstr "``0.5``：典型的木材或桌面摩擦。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:56
msgid "``0.8``: rubber-like, objects stop almost immediately."
msgstr "``0.8``：类似橡胶，物体几乎立即停止。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:57
msgid "``>1.0``: extreme values, objects barely move without a strong push."
msgstr "``>1.0``：极高摩擦，物体几乎不会移动，除非受到较大的推动。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:62
msgid "Bounce"
msgstr "弹性（Bounce）"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:63
msgid ""
"The **Bounce** parameter defines how much energy is preserved in a "
"collision, also known as the *Coefficient of Restitution (e)*. It only "
"affects motion along the collision normal, not along the surface."
msgstr ""
"**Bounce（弹性）** 用于定义碰撞时能量保留的比例，也称为 **恢复系数（Coefficient of Restitution, "
"e）**。该参数只影响碰撞法线方向的速度，不影响沿表面方向的运动。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:66
msgid "e = \\frac{v_{after}}{v_{before}}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:72
msgid ""
"``0.0``: perfectly inelastic — the object sticks to the surface (like "
"clay)."
msgstr "``0.0``：完全非弹性碰撞 —— 物体会粘在表面上（类似黏土）。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:73
msgid ""
"``1.0``: perfectly elastic — the object bounces back with the same speed "
"(idealized)."
msgstr "``1.0``：完全弹性碰撞 —— 物体会以相同速度反弹（理想情况）。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:74
msgid "``0.0 ~ 1.0``: partially elastic, some energy is lost."
msgstr "``0.0 ~ 1.0``：部分弹性碰撞，会损失一部分能量。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:79
msgid "Linear Damping"
msgstr "线性阻尼（Linear Damping）"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:80
msgid ""
"**Linear Damping** simulates drag forces (like air resistance) that slow "
"down an object's motion when no external force is applied. It gradually "
"reduces the object's linear velocity."
msgstr "**Linear Damping（线性阻尼）** 用于模拟阻力（例如空气阻力）。当没有外力作用时，它会逐渐降低物体的线性速度。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:85
msgid "``0.0``: no damping — the object slides forever, like on ice."
msgstr "``0.0``：没有阻尼 —— 物体会像在冰面上一样持续滑动。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:86
msgid "``0.04`` (default): slight drag, objects slowly come to rest."
msgstr "``0.04`` （默认）：轻微阻力，物体会逐渐停止。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:87
msgid "``0.3``: noticeable drag, objects stop within a few seconds."
msgstr "``0.3``：明显阻力，物体会在几秒内停止。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:88
msgid "``1.0``: immediate stop, objects lose velocity almost instantly."
msgstr "``1.0``：几乎立即停止。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:93
msgid "Angular Damping"
msgstr "角阻尼（Angular Damping）"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:94
msgid ""
"**Angular Damping** controls how quickly an object's rotation slows down."
" It works the same way as :ref:`linear-damping`, but affects angular "
"velocity instead of linear velocity."
msgstr ""
"**Angular Damping（角阻尼）** 控制物体旋转速度衰减的速度。它的作用方式与 :ref:`线性阻尼（Linear Damping）"
" <linear-damping>` 相同，但影响的是角速度，而不是线速度。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:99
msgid "``0.0``: spins like a top, never slows down."
msgstr "``0.0``：像陀螺一样持续旋转，不会减速。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:100
msgid "``0.1`` (default): slight rotational drag, spin fades over time."
msgstr "``0.1`` （默认）：轻微旋转阻力，旋转会逐渐减弱。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:101
msgid "``0.3``: strong drag, object stops rotating in a few seconds."
msgstr "``0.3``：较强阻力，旋转会在几秒内停止。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:102
msgid "``1.0``: rotation stops almost immediately."
msgstr "``1.0``：几乎立即停止旋转。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:105
msgid "Add Rigid Body"
msgstr "添加刚体"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:108
msgid "Quick Add"
msgstr "快速添加"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:109
msgid "Select the **Armature** and switch to *Pose Mode*."
msgstr "选择 **骨架**，并切换到 *姿态模式*。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:110
msgid "Choose the bone(s) that should receive a Rigid Body."
msgstr "选择需要添加刚体的骨骼。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:111
msgid "Click the :menuselection:`+` button"
msgstr "点击 :menuselection:`+` 按钮。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:112
msgid "Configure the properties and press :menuselection:`OK` to confirm."
msgstr "设置相关属性后，点击 :menuselection:`OK` 确认。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:120
msgid ""
"You can find detailed explanations of all rigid body parameters in "
":ref:`Rigid Body Properties <rigid_body_properties>`."
msgstr "所有刚体参数的详细说明可以在 :ref:`刚体属性 <rigid_body_properties>` 部分查看。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:121
msgid ""
"``$name`` is a placeholder that will use the name of the target bone as "
"the rigid body's name."
msgstr "``$name`` 是一个占位符，会自动使用目标骨骼的名称作为刚体名称。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:122
msgid ""
"When no bone is selected in *Pose Mode*, the add-on creates an "
":ref:`Auxiliary Rigid Body <auxiliary_rigid_bodies>` for the model."
msgstr "如果在 *姿态模式* 中没有选中任何骨骼，插件会为模型创建一个 :ref:`辅助刚体 <auxiliary_rigid_bodies>`。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:123
msgid ""
"You can adjust the :ref:`Rigid Body Properties <rigid_body_properties>` "
"at any time in the :ref:`Rigid Body Properties Panel "
"<rigid_body_properties_panel>`."
msgstr ""
"你可以随时在 :ref:`刚体属性面板 <rigid_body_properties_panel>` 中修改 :ref:`刚体属性 "
"<rigid_body_properties>`。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:125
msgid "For **Rigify** armatures, it is recommended to:"
msgstr "对于 **Rigify** 骨架，建议采用以下方式："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:126
msgid ""
"Attach rigid bodies of type ``Bone`` (i.e., fully bone-driven rigid "
"bodies) to the ``DEF-`` bones."
msgstr "将 ``Bone`` 类型的刚体（即完全由骨骼驱动的刚体）绑定到 ``DEF-`` 骨骼。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:128
msgid ""
"You can move and rotate the rigid bodies freely (in 3D viewport), and "
"scale them (through the :ref:`Rigid Body Properties Panel "
"<rigid_body_properties_panel>` ), to fit the model's mesh contour as "
"closely as possible and achieve more accurate physical simulation."
msgstr ""
"你可以在 *3D视图* 中自由移动和旋转刚体，并在 :ref:`刚体属性面板 <rigid_body_properties_panel>` "
"中调整尺寸，使其尽可能贴合模型的网格轮廓，从而获得更准确的物理模拟效果。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:131
msgid ""
"A single bone can drive multiple rigid bodies of this type, all of which "
"follow the same bone transform."
msgstr "一个骨骼可以驱动多个此类型的刚体，这些刚体都会跟随同一个骨骼的变换。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:136
msgid ""
"Attach rigid bodies of type ``Physics`` or ``Physics + Bone`` (i.e., "
"physics-driven rigid bodies) to the ``CTRL-`` bones."
msgstr "将 ``Physics`` 或 ``Physics + Bone`` 类型的刚体（即由物理系统驱动的刚体）绑定到 ``CTRL-`` 骨骼。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:138
msgid ""
"To allow manual correction of physics results, two **Bone Collections** "
"are required:"
msgstr "为了允许在物理模拟后进行手动修正，需要创建两个骨骼集合（Bone Collections）："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:140
msgid ""
"one named ``xxx_Physics`` that stores the bones directly controlled by "
"the physics system, and another that mirrors their rotation via ``Copy "
"Rotation`` and uses ``Mix Before Original`` to support manual adjustments"
" for fixing minor penetrations or undesirable motion."
msgstr ""
"其中一个命名为 ``xxx_Physics``，用于存放直接由物理系统驱动的骨骼；另一个集合通过 ``Copy Rotation`` "
"约束复制其旋转，并使用 ``Mix Before Original`` 模式，从而允许在其基础上进行手动调整，修正一些轻微的穿插或不理想的运动。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:144
msgid ""
"This modular structure helps isolate and debug issues efficiently. For "
"details on creating such bone collections and adding custom ones to a "
"Rigify Armature:"
msgstr "这种模块化结构有助于快速定位和调试问题。关于如何创建这些骨骼集合以及在 Rigify 骨架中添加自定义集合的详细方法："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:147
msgid ""
"Check |youtube_link| or |bilibili_link| for the tutorial, or refer to the"
" setup shown in the sample file. (**Note**: You may focus only on the "
"part of the video demonstrating how to add bone collections; the cloth "
"simulation section can be ignored.)"
msgstr ""
"可以参考 |youtube_link| 或 |bilibili_link| "
"中的教程，或者查看示例文件中的设置。（**注意**：只需关注视频中如何添加 Bone Collection 的部分，布料模拟部分可以忽略）"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:158
msgid ""
"For ``Physics`` or ``Physics + Bone`` type rigid bodies, a single bone "
"can also be bound to multiple rigid bodies. During simulation, the bone "
"will be driven by the rigid body with the greatest mass, while the others"
" act as auxiliary bodies."
msgstr ""
"对于 ``Physics`` 或 ``Physics + Bone`` 类型的刚体，一个骨骼同样可以绑定多个刚体。在模拟过程中，骨骼会由 "
"**质量最大的刚体** 驱动，其余刚体则作为辅助刚体参与计算。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:162
msgid ""
"With other rigs or custom armatures, make sure that all bones "
"participating in the physics simulation have corresponding **control "
"bones**, allowing you to override the simulation when necessary and "
"prevent mesh intersections or penetrations."
msgstr ""
"对于其他绑定系统或自定义骨架，请确保所有参与物理模拟的骨骼都具有对应的 "
"**控制骨骼**。这样在必要时你可以手动覆盖物理模拟结果，从而避免网格发生相交或穿插。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:168
msgid "Save Presets"
msgstr "保存预设"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:169
msgid ""
"You can save presets for reuse. This workflow is very useful in practice,"
" as it can save a significant amount of time!"
msgstr "你可以保存参数预设以便重复使用。在实际工作中，这种方式可以显著节省时间。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:179
msgid "Rigid Body Properties"
msgstr "刚体属性"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:181
msgid "**Name**: The name of the Rigid Body."
msgstr "**Name**：刚体名称。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:182
msgid "**Collision Group**: Collision group assigned to this object."
msgstr "**Collision Group**：该刚体所属的碰撞组。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:183
msgid ""
"**Collision Group Mask**: Groups that this object should **Not** collide "
"with."
msgstr "**Collision Group Mask**：**不会** 与该刚体发生碰撞的组。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:184
msgid "**Rigid Type**:"
msgstr "**Rigid Type（刚体类型）：**"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:186
msgid "``Bone``: The rigid body follows the orientation of the attached bone."
msgstr "``Bone``：刚体跟随绑定骨骼的变换。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:187
msgid "``Physics``: The bone's transform is fully driven by the rigid body."
msgstr "``Physics``：骨骼的变换完全由刚体驱动。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:188
msgid ""
"``Physics + Bone``: The bone's position follows its parent, but its "
"rotation is copied from the rigid body."
msgstr "``Physics + Bone``：骨骼位置仍然跟随父骨骼，但旋转来自刚体。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:190
msgid "**Shape**: Collision shape type."
msgstr "**Shape**：碰撞体形状。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:191
msgid "**Outward Axis**: Local bone axis that points \"outward\"."
msgstr "**Outward Axis**：骨骼局部坐标中指向“外侧”的轴。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:192
msgid ""
"**Size**: Dimensions of the collision shape, scaled relative to the "
"target bone length."
msgstr "**Size**：碰撞体尺寸，相对于目标骨骼的长度进行缩放。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:193
msgid "**Mass**: :ref:`Mass <mass>`."
msgstr "**Mass**：:ref:`质量（Mass） <mass>`。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:194
msgid "**Friction**: :ref:`Friction <friction>`."
msgstr "**Friction**：:ref:`摩擦力（Friction） <friction>`。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:195
msgid "**Bounce**: :ref:`Bounce <bounce>`."
msgstr "**Bounce**：:ref:`弹性（Bounce） <bounce>`。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:196
msgid "**Linear Damping**: :ref:`Linear Damping <linear-damping>`."
msgstr "**Linear Damping**：:ref:`线性阻尼（Linear Damping） <linear-damping>`。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:197
msgid "**Angular Damping**: :ref:`Angular Damping <angular-damping>`."
msgstr "**Angular Damping**：:ref:`角阻尼（Angular Damping） <angular-damping>`."

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:200
msgid ""
"When modifying rigid body properties, always use the add-on's :ref:`Rigid"
" Body Properties Panel <rigid_body_properties_panel>`. Do not edit them "
"through Blender's built-in interface."
msgstr ""
"修改刚体属性时，请始终使用本插件提供的 :ref:`刚体属性面板 <rigid_body_properties_panel>`，不要通过 "
"Blender 内置界面直接编辑。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:204
msgid "``Physics`` vs ``Physics + Bone``"
msgstr "``Physics`` 与 ``Physics + Bone``"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:205
msgid ""
"``Physics``: The bone's location and rotation are completely determined "
"by the rigid body. The rigid body may move the bone away from the "
"Armature."
msgstr "``Physics``：骨骼的位置和旋转完全由刚体控制。刚体可能会使骨骼偏离骨架。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:206
msgid ""
"``Physics + Bone``: The bone's position is still driven by its parent, "
"but its rotation is copied from the rigid body. This prevents the bone "
"from detaching while still inheriting the physical simulation results."
msgstr "``Physics + Bone``：骨骼的位置仍由父骨驱动，但旋转从刚体复制。这样可以在保持物理模拟结果的同时，防止骨骼脱离父骨。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:208
msgid "``Outward Axis``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:209
msgid ""
"When using **box-shaped** rigid bodies (**sphere** or **capsule** shapes "
"can ignore this setting) to simulate skirt physics, make sure that the "
"target bones already have the correct local orientation — either **Z "
"Outward** or **X Outward**."
msgstr ""
"在使用 **盒状** 刚体（**球形** 或 **胶囊形** 刚体可忽略此设置）模拟裙子物理时，请确保目标骨骼已经具有正确的局部方向——即 "
"**Z轴向外** 或 **X轴向外**。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:213
msgid ""
"Then, when adding the rigid body, simply set ``Outward Axis`` to ``Z`` or"
" ``X`` accordingly."
msgstr "然后，在添加刚体时，将 ``Outward Axis`` 设置为相应的 ``Z`` 或 ``X``。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:215
msgid ""
"This ensures that the newly added rigid body inherits the correct initial"
" rotation:"
msgstr "这样可以确保新添加的刚体继承正确的初始旋转："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:217
msgid "The **Z-axis** aligns with the bone direction,"
msgstr "**Z 轴** 与骨骼方向对齐；"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:218
msgid "The **Y-axis** points outward along the skirt's normal,"
msgstr "**Y 轴** 沿裙子法线指向外侧；"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:219
msgid "The **X-axis** runs tangentially along the skirt surface."
msgstr "**X 轴** 沿裙子表面切向延伸。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst
msgid "Comparison: Correct vs Incorrect Setup"
msgstr "对比：正确设置与错误设置"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:225
msgid "Correct bone orientation with matching Outward Axis"
msgstr "正确的骨骼方向及匹配的 Outward Axis"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:230
msgid "**Correct Setup** — The rigid body aligns perfectly with the mesh."
msgstr "**正确设置** — 刚体与网格完美对齐。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:232
msgid "Incorrect bone orientation or mismatched Outward Axis"
msgstr "骨骼方向错误或 Outward Axis 不匹配"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:237
msgid "**Incorrect Setup** — The rigid body appears twisted or offset."
msgstr "**错误设置** — 刚体出现扭曲或偏移。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:239
msgid "**Size**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:240
msgid ""
"In the preset panel, all shapes have three components (``x, y, z``). "
"However, the number of components required varies by shape:"
msgstr "在预设面板中，所有形状都有三个分量（``x, y, z``）。但是，不同形状需要的分量数量不同："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:243
msgid "*Sphere*: only radius (use ``x``)."
msgstr "*球体*：仅半径（使用 ``x``）。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:244
msgid "*Box*: width, height, depth (use ``x, y, z``)."
msgstr "*盒体*：长、宽、高（使用 ``x, y, z``）。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:245
msgid "*Capsule*: radius (hemisphere) and height (use ``x, y``)."
msgstr "*胶囊体*：半径（半球）和高度（使用 ``x, y``）。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:247
msgid ""
"It is recommended to keep the default values in the preset panel and make"
" any necessary fine-tuning in the :ref:`Rigid Body Properties Panel "
"<rigid_body_properties_panel>`."
msgstr "建议保持预设面板中的默认值，并在 :ref:`刚体属性面板 <rigid_body_properties_panel>` 中进行必要的微调。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:253
msgid "Rigid Body Properties Panel"
msgstr "刚体属性面板"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:255
msgid ""
"The *Rigid Body Properties Panel* is where you can view and edit rigid "
"body attributes. It can be found under the *Physics Tab* in Blender."
msgstr "*刚体属性面板* 用于查看和编辑刚体属性。该面板位于 Blender 的 *Physics* 选项卡中。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:265
msgid ""
"For consistency and to avoid unintended errors, all rigid body attributes"
" **Must** be modified via the add-on's *Rigid Body Properties Panel*."
msgstr "为了保持一致性并避免意外错误，所有刚体属性 **必须** 通过插件提供的 *刚体属性面板* 进行修改。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:269
msgid ""
"Some properties can still be edited through Blender's default UI, and "
"these actions cannot be blocked. For example:"
msgstr "某些属性仍可通过 Blender 的内置界面进行编辑，这些操作无法被阻止。例如："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:272
msgid ""
"Physical parameters such as :ref:`Mass <mass>` and :ref:`Friction "
"<friction>` can still be edited in the *Physics Tab*."
msgstr "物理参数，如 :ref:`质量 <mass>` 和 :ref:`摩擦力 <friction>`，仍可在 *物理选项卡* 中编辑。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:273
msgid "Scaling a rigid body in the 3D viewport with the :menuselection:`S` key."
msgstr "在 *3D视图* 中使用 :menuselection:`S` 键缩放刚体。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:275
msgid ""
"However, editing through Blender's defaults will bypass the add-on's "
"callbacks. These callbacks may perform important tasks such as updating "
"data, reassigning materials, or adjusting constraints."
msgstr "然而，通过 Blender 内置操作编辑刚体将绕过插件的回调，这些回调可能执行某些关键任务，如更新数据、重新分配材质或调整约束等。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:278
msgid "**Example - Scaling in the 3D viewport:**"
msgstr "**示例 - 在 3D 视图中缩放:**"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:280
msgid ""
"Using the :menuselection:`S` key only changes the **Visible Mesh**, the "
"internal size data remains unchanged. This can cause the **Visual Mesh** "
"and the **Collision Shape** to diverge, leading to clipping or "
"misalignment."
msgstr ""
"使用 :menuselection:`S` 键仅会改变 **可视网格**，内部尺寸数据仍保持不变。这可能导致 **可视网格** 与实际 "
"**碰撞形状** 不一致，引发穿模或错位。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:286
msgid "Rigid Body List"
msgstr "刚体列表"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:288
msgid "The *Rigid Body List* shows all rigid bodies in the current scene."
msgstr "*刚体列表* 显示当前场景中的所有刚体。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:290
msgid ""
"By default, it filters by :menuselection:`Active Model`, displaying only "
"the rigid bodies of the currently selected model. To view rigid bodies "
"from all models, change the filter to :menuselection:`All Models`."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下会按照 :menuselection:`Active Model` "
"进行筛选，只显示当前选中模型的刚体。如果需要查看所有模型的刚体，可以将筛选切换为 :menuselection:`All Models`。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:299
msgid "Reordering List Items"
msgstr "重新排序列表项"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:300
msgid ""
"You can reorder list items using the :menuselection:`⬆` and "
":menuselection:`⬇` buttons, or through the right-side dropdown menu "
"options: :menuselection:`Move To Top` and :menuselection:`Move To "
"Bottom`."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用 :menuselection:`⬆` 和 :menuselection:`⬇` 按钮重新排列列表项，也可以通过右侧下拉菜单中的 "
":menuselection:`Move To Top` 和 :menuselection:`Move To Bottom` 选项进行排序。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:309
msgid "Error Indicators"
msgstr "错误提示"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:312
msgid "Missing Physics"
msgstr "缺少 Physics 组件"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:313
msgid ""
"A list item will show a *\"Missing Physics\"* icon when its rigid body "
"has no *Rigid Body Settings* component. To fix this, use the "
":menuselection:`Add Rigid Body` button in the :ref:`Rigid Body Properties"
" Panel <rigid_body_properties_panel>` to restore the settings."
msgstr ""
"当刚体对象缺少 *Rigid Body Settings* 组件时，对应的列表项会显示 *\"缺少物理组件\"* 图标。要修复此问题，可以在 "
":ref:`刚体属性面板 <rigid_body_properties_panel>` 中点击 :menuselection:`Add Rigid"
" Body` 按钮以恢复该设置。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:322
msgid "Missing Bone"
msgstr "缺少骨骼"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:323
msgid ""
"A list item will show a *\"Missing Bone\"* icon when its rigid body has "
"no assigned bone. The missing bone can be reassigned in the :ref:`Rigid "
"Body Properties Panel <rigid_body_properties_panel>`."
msgstr ""
"当刚体没有绑定骨骼时，对应的列表项会显示 *\"缺少骨骼\"* 图标。你可以在 :ref:`刚体属性面板 "
"<rigid_body_properties_panel>` 中重新分配骨骼。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:334
msgid "Select Rigid Bodies"
msgstr "选择刚体"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:336
msgid ""
"You can quickly perform batch selection of rigid bodies through "
":menuselection:`Select Similar` in the right-side menu. This tool "
"compares the properties of the active rigid body and selects all other "
"rigid bodies that share the same values."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过右侧菜单中的 :menuselection:`Select Similar` "
"快速批量选择刚体。该工具会比较当前激活刚体的属性，并选择所有具有相同属性值的其他刚体。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:340
msgid "Properties for Comparison"
msgstr "匹配属性"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:342
msgid ""
"When invoking **Select Similar**, a pop-up dialog will appear, allowing "
"you to choose which properties should be matched:"
msgstr "点击 :menuselection:`Select Similar` 后，会弹出一个对话框，允许你选择用于匹配的属性："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:344
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Collision Group`: Selects rigid bodies that share the "
"same collision group number."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Collision Group`：选择具有相同碰撞组编号的刚体。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:345
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Collision Group Mask`: Selects rigid bodies that have the"
" same collision mask configuration."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Collision Group Mask`：选择具有相同碰撞掩码配置的刚体。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:346
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Rigid Type`: Selects rigid bodies that have the same "
"rigid body type (e.g., ``Bone``, ``Physics``, ``Physics + Bone``)."
msgstr ""
":menuselection:`Rigid Type`：选择具有相同刚体类型的刚体（例如 "
"``Bone``、``Physics``、``Physics + Bone``）。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:347
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Shape`: Selects rigid bodies that use the same collision "
"shape."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Shape`：选择使用相同碰撞体形状的刚体。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:348
msgid ":menuselection:`Bone`: Selects rigid bodies bound to the same target bone."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Bone`：选择绑定到同一目标骨骼的刚体。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:350
msgid "These properties can be selected individually or in any combination."
msgstr "这些属性可以单独选择，也可以任意组合使用。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:358
msgid "Hide Others"
msgstr "隐藏其他对象"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:360
msgid "The dialog also includes a *Hide Others* option:"
msgstr "该对话框还包含一个 *Hide Others* 选项："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:362
msgid ""
"When enabled, all rigid bodies that do not match the chosen properties "
"will be hidden."
msgstr "启用后，所有不符合所选属性条件的刚体都会被隐藏。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:363
msgid ""
"When disabled, unmatched objects remain visible but are simply not "
"selected."
msgstr "关闭后，不符合条件的对象仍然保持可见，但不会被选中。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:368
msgid "Remove Rigid Body"
msgstr "删除刚体"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:370
msgid ""
"Select a rigid body in the *3D viewport*, the *Rigid Body List*, or the "
"*Outliner*, then click the :menuselection:`-` button to remove it."
msgstr "在 *3D视图*、*刚体列表* 或 *大纲视图* 中选择刚体，然后点击 :menuselection:`-` 按钮即可删除。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:380
msgid "Example: Auxiliary Rigid Bodies"
msgstr "示例：辅助刚体"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:382
msgid ""
"When adding rigid bodies to the hair of a stylized character — especially"
" for curved bangs or side locks — simply assigning a single rigid body to"
" each bone often leads to an undesired effect:"
msgstr "在为风格化角色的头发添加刚体时（特别是弯曲的刘海或侧发），如果每个骨骼只使用一个刚体，往往会产生不理想的效果："

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:385
msgid "The hair strands will hang straight down under gravity during simulation."
msgstr "在模拟过程中，头发会在重力作用下垂直下垂。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:387
msgid ""
"However, stylized (non-realistic) hair should retain its designed shape "
"and elasticity even in an **Idle** state. To reproduce this elastic "
"behavior and maintain a smooth, natural motion during simulation, we "
"introduce *Auxiliary Rigid Bodies* that influence the target Rigid "
"Bodies, helping them maintain their intended modeled pose instead of "
"collapsing under gravity."
msgstr ""
"但对于非写实的风格化头发，即使在 **Idle** "
"状态下，也应该保持设计时的形状和弹性。为了重现这种弹性效果，并在模拟过程中保持平滑自然的运动，我们引入 *辅助刚体* "
"来影响目标刚体，使其能够维持建模时的姿态，而不是在重力作用下直接下垂。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:392
msgid ""
"The *Auxiliary Rigid Body* usually has the same mass as its target. By "
"adjusting the **Angle** between them, or the **Length** of the *Auxiliary"
" Rigid Body*, you can control the amount of torque it applies to the "
"target and achieve the desired balance in simulation."
msgstr ""
"*辅助刚体* 通常与其目标刚体具有相同的质量。通过调整它们之间的 **角度**，或 *辅助刚体* 的 "
"**长度**，你可以控制其对目标刚体施加的扭矩，从而在模拟中达到期望的平衡效果。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:397
msgid "Comparison: With vs. Without Auxiliary Rigid Bodies"
msgstr "对比：使用辅助刚体 与 不使用辅助刚体"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:398
msgid "Correct setup with auxiliary Rigid Body"
msgstr "使用辅助刚体的正确设置"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:403
msgid ""
"**With Auxiliary Rigid Body** — The target rigid body is supported by an "
"angled *Auxiliary Rigid Body*, maintaining the stylized curvature and "
"preventing it from drooping under gravity."
msgstr "**使用辅助刚体** — 目标刚体由一个带角度的辅助刚体提供支撑，从而保持风格化的形状，防止其在重力作用下下垂。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:406
msgid "Setup without auxiliary Rigid Body"
msgstr "未使用辅助刚体的设置"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:411
msgid ""
"**Without Auxiliary Rigid Body** — The target Rigid Body is only "
"constrained by gravity, causing the hair to fall straight down and lose "
"its designed curvature."
msgstr "**未使用辅助刚体** — 目标刚体仅受到重力约束，导致头发在模拟中直接下垂，并失去原本设计的弯曲形状。"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:414
msgid "MMD model example using auxiliary Rigid Bodies"
msgstr "使用辅助刚体的 MMD 模型示例"

#: ../../source/rigidbody.rst:419
msgid ""
"**MMD Model Example** — The “Nico” model uses multiple *Auxiliary Rigid "
"Bodies* on the hair, keeping the hair elastic and lifted even in the idle"
" pose."
msgstr "**MMD 模型示例** — “妮可”模型在头发上使用了大量辅助刚体，使头发即使在 **Idle** 姿态下也能保持弹性和上扬的形状。"

